{"tid":1079322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"真係香港？馬路邊化妝影相　網民：咪害司機","createTime":"2019-03-27T01:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T01:32:16.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"79b807c2d6572aaf9c67321083c05be4a761699f","tid":1079322,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T01:07:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190327/photo/bkn-20190327081537411-0327_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190327081839\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190327%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190327081537411-0327_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190327081839&h=d79ae1a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬路趣事多籮籮。近日在旺角和油塘分別出現馬路奇觀，到底是甚麼事？<br />\n<br />\n有網民於周一（25日）發貼指在登打士街近廣華醫院附近，有三名內地青年手持單鏡反光相機又趴又蹲，在馬路邊舉機拍照。有網民大感困惑：「有咩影？」，又有人斥：「咪害啲司機啦」！ <br />\n<br />\n同日，另有網民發貼指在茶果嶺道近天后廟，一名大媽竟坐在安全島上疑似化妝，更伸出雙腳，途經司機見狀紛紛收油慢駛。 <br />\n<br />\n有網民建議：「見到不如報警啦，無論佢係咩原因咁樣，報警搵人嚟處理，對佢同其他馬路使用者都更好」，有人揶揄：「撩美腿，截便車」、「佢覺得安全島真係好安全？」 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190327/photo/bkn-20190327081537411-0327_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190327081839\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190327%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190327081537411-0327_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190327081839&h=8f84488d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190327/photo/bkn-20190327081537411-0327_00822_001_04p.jpg?20190327081839\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190327%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190327081537411-0327_00822_001_04p.jpg%3F20190327081839&h=3fb91add&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190327/bkn-20190327081537411-0327_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190327%2Fbkn-20190327081537411-0327_00822_001.html&d=vajnz719fThxN7XVIZyF5aEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=f7cfae60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190327/bkn-20190327081537411-0327_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b4e325f293e903c93dfec5b9e419e17ae89664f4","tid":1079322,"uid":57376,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T01:15:04.000Z","msg":"支那人成日做咁多核突野仲好意思話人歧視佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22cb41a36f676edee6d461e578170d1ce1a01476","tid":1079322,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T01:17:07.000Z","msg":"又話包容文化，定係報新聞搏收視就唔使包容"},{"pid":"b35a6b51c1e93575d15309f887c726dbf1474c6d","tid":1079322,"uid":152476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T01:24:38.000Z","msg":"見到d動作就知係支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"368679ea102768e98d7f4702c341d3f2ccb93877","tid":1079322,"uid":176472,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T01:28:30.000Z","msg":"旺角條大陸妹企出界輾爆腳<br />\n巴士司機判兩年 屌佢啦"},{"pid":"8b87a8e6550984b813bdd4c3b250e7ab4775161f","tid":1079322,"uid":175661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T01:32:16.000Z","msg":"真係香港?好大陸呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}